verbose_text: We further demonstrated that the blockade of IL-17A inhibited atrial fibrosis and decreased the level of Col-1, Col-3 and alpha-SMA in the rats with SP, similar to the effects reported in models of cardiac infarction and myocarditis induced cardiac fibrosis, and consistent with a potential role for IL-17A in cardiac fibrosis.
evidence: level of Col-1, Col-3 and alpha-SMA
